probably the greatest.

00:00:52.770 --> 00:00:56.540
The Aztecs formed out of an alliance of three
major cities in modern day Mexico in about

00:00:56.540 --> 00:01:01.010
1430, just 89 years before Cortez and his
conquistadors showed up.

00:01:01.010 --> 00:01:04.690
The Aztec state was very hierarchical, with
an emperor at the top and a group of unruly

00:01:04.690 --> 00:01:08.610
