00:07:05.530 --> 00:07:08.490
That led to a period of wealth and national
pride, which meant that people had both the

00:07:08.490 --> 00:07:14.160
money and the desire to see, I don’t know,
plays about old English Kings named Richard. And that,

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:19.120
