00:08:58.380 --> 00:09:02.170
rich. The Ming government also failed to peg
taxes to inflation, and spent too much on

00:09:02.170 --> 00:09:03.700
defense, notably the Great Wall.

00:09:03.700 --> 00:09:07.880
